==English==
===Expression===
'''[[see]] [[a]] [[man]] [[about]] a [[horse]]''' {{idiom}}

#{{slang}} {{idiom}} {{euphemism}} (''euphemistic'') to [[urinate]] (''used mainly of men'')
#:''Wait for me here. I'll only be a couple of minutes. I've just got to '''see a man about a horse'''.''

